Title: A METHODOLOGY FOR QUERY REFORMULATION IN CIS USING SEMANTIC KNOWLEDGE  
Author: DANIELA FLORESCU and LOUIQA RASCHID and PATRICK VALDURIEZ M. and Singh, M.P.) 
Keyword: mediators, query rewriting, integrity constraints, object query languages.  
Address: Rocquencourt, 78153 Le Chesnay Cedex, France  College Park, MD 20742  Rocquencourt, 78153 Le Chesnay Cedex, France  
Affiliation: INRIA  University of Maryland,  INRIA  
